<title>BELGIUM: EU's Santer &quot;encourages&quot; Renault court case.</title>
<headline>EU's Santer &quot;encourages&quot; Renault court case.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1997-03-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>A statement by European Commission President Jacques Santer criticising French car maker Renault's closure of a Belgian plant could be seen as support for the company to be taken to court, his spokesman said.</p>
<p>&quot;You can take that as encouragement,&quot; said Nikolaus van der Pas, Santer's spokesman, when asked by reporters if the Commission thought Renault had a case to answer.</p>
